	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The PG Tomo, is a kickass axe, the dmg is pretty fair, and the delay is also ok, however the best thing of this axe is the beserker strength, its a random cast during a fight, and can last from 3 seconds to arround 10. U can get it several times during a fight. Once your muscles goes beserk, u loose 20 points in Agile, but gain 10 % more strength, u hit harder and faster in the first round. Like thats not enough, u also are imortal towards hits, spells, poisen ect, during the beserk effect. I had many of these Tomos, and I must say its still one of the best 1hand Axes in the game. However im only lvl 26 and switched to the Silver War Axe instead. The PG tomo is found in Highpass hold on a named Gnoll, Mucktail.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
