	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				To clarifly things on the PGT.  It is on Grenix Mucktail which is in Highpass Hold, gnoll side.  He spawns about every 2-6 hours, but sometimes can spawn twice an hour, its almost totally random.  To get it, you need a caster, particulary a wizard.  Grenix is lvl 21-22, but his weapon makes it a level 25 MOB if you are melee'ing it.  <BR>
<BR>
The bezerker str goes off depending on your dex and level, I am level 21 and have 76 dex, and I've had it go off twice in one quick battle, and sometimes doesn't go off for up to 3 battles, its pretty much random, but dex and lvl does help.  I found this out becuase I have a friend who has ~90 dex and it goes off almost twice as much.  <BR>
<BR>
On the cost of the PGT, I've seen them go for 250pp+ on Quellious. Normally you need to camp it, becuase most people won't sell it, its that good )<BR>
<BR>
Uzunus Lifebearer-Holy Paladin on Quellious
				</font>
