	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This item is found in Highpass Hold near the West Gate on a named gnoll called Grenix Mucktail. He is a Level 20-24 Gnoll and will always have the PGT. The spawn rate on him and his brother Venven (which carries the Cracked Darkwood Shield (AC 12, +9 STR)) is between 15 minutes to 6 hours. If you're a Warrior, prepare to spend about a week getting it unless you're in a group with a caster. Casters have a clean break on this one, being able to steal it quickly from Warriors. I spent about a week and a half getting this weapon, and it's well worth the time. I'm a Level 22 Warrior on the Povar server, and getting this item was pure hell for me. If you want a lot of power though, combine this with the Cracked Darkwood Shield found on Venven Mucktail (in the same area, see above) for a long 1H Slash ride. :)
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
